<p>
<lb n="1"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> rac coḻarum koṅkil keṅkai koṇṭa
<lb n="2"/>nāṉa kāṭuveṭṭikaḷum viṭaiyil Araiyan rā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>rā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>
<lb n="3"/>ṉ pāṇṭiyanārum kumaraṉ civacaraṇattūrāṉa kaliṅkattaraiya
<lb n="4"/>rum veḷāṉ tirunilakaṇṭa nārāṉa vi<hi rend="grantha">rarāje<unclear>ntra</unclear></hi>varakuṇa
<lb n="5"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> rā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>rum Araiyaṉ tiruvekampa nāraṇa cenāvaraiyarum cā <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="6"/>ttan pūtiyārāṉa Īḻattaraiyarum Eva Ivarkale viṉa paṭi
<lb n="7"/>ye Uṭaṉ kūṭṭattu Atikārikaḷ naraciṅka cantira pū<hi rend="grantha">ṣa</hi>ṇ
<lb n="8"/>nārāna vi<hi rend="grantha">rarāje</hi>n<hi rend="grantha">tra brāhmāyrāja</hi> kūṭi <hi rend="grantha">tri</hi>yacikāmaṇi va
<lb n="9"/>ḷa nāṭṭu paṉaiyūr nāṭṭu <hi rend="grantha">je</hi>yaṅkoṇṭa coḻa nallūruṭaiyā
<lb n="10"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> kūttāṭiyārāna vi<hi rend="grantha">rarājendra</hi>
